  "detailed_description": "Simple VR Archery shooting game. Defend yourself against the oncoming enemies with arrows. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn addition to the basic arrows, use two types of Trap Arrows.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTake advantage of Scope to easily kill distant enemies.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDefend your ranged attacks with shields.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFinally defend your stronghold with enemy attacks.<br />\r\n(Watch out for hidden enemies.)",
